<h1>Simple MDE dummy app</h1>

<h2>Using change action method</h2>
{{simple-mde value=value change="showNewValue"}}
<p> New Value : </p>
{{simple-mde-preview newValue}}

<h2>Using mut action method</h2>
{{simple-mde value=value change=(action (mut value))}}
<p> Value : </p>
{{simple-mde-preview value}}
<p> link a textarea </p>
{{textarea value=value}}

<h2>Passing options to the simpleMDE instance</h2>
{{simple-mde value=value options=simpleMdeOptions}}
